race.comment: PRECIOUS GIRL (7) finished runner up at all three runs this time in and shapes as the main danger. No match for Trumper over this track and trip in a Super Maiden at latest. Go close. UNCLE BARRY (1) winkers come off and back in trip after he gripped on late when fourth over 1180m at Gundagai. Best form stacks up despite drawing out. DORALEE (2) massive run first up and she gets a better set-up here. Covered ground from the wide gate when second over 1000m at Kembla Grange. Will tag the good tempo and no shock to see her shed her Maiden status. BOBBY (6) improving with racing and stays in the calculations.
